### Get Events

GET {{rooturl}}/api/events/list

### Options Events

OPTIONS {{rooturl}}/api/events/list

### Get Tracks

@trackSearchTerm = david guetta

GET {{rooturl}}/api/tracks/search?query={{trackSearchTerm}}

### Options Tracks

OPTIONS {{rooturl}}/api/tracks/search?query={{trackSearchTerm}}

### Delete Cache
DELETE {{rooturl}}/api/events/deletecache
x-ms-client-principal: {{fakeprincipal}}

### Make Requesst
POST {{rooturl}}/api/musicrequest/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "eventId":"459c5d02-2c58-41ff-856b-8f410317fee9",
    "musicRequest":"Test no bpm or time",
    "requestedBy":"From The Floor",
    "bpm": null,
    "time":""
}

### Make Request with string bpm
POST {{rooturl}}/api/musicrequest/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "eventId":"459c5d02-2c58-41ff-856b-8f410317fee9",
    "musicRequest":"Test string bpm",
    "requestedBy":"From The Floor",
    "bpm": "116.0",
    "time":""
}

### Submit Contact Form
POST {{rooturl}}/api/contact/submit
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Test Visitor",
    "email": "visitor@example.com",
    "subject": "DJ hire enquiry",
    "message": "Hi Mark, are you available for a birthday event?",
    "company": "",
    "elapsedMs": 8000
}

